     Each TLS callback RVA now promotes to a BinaryFunction
     with kind_detail=tls_persistence + tls_callback=true.
     Edge: pe → bin_func. TLS callbacks are real functions that
     run before main() — common malware persistence vector.
     They now participate in PageRank / centrality and are
