  Action count: 163 (unchanged — promotions added to existing
  actions, no new actions). EntityKinds: 29 → 30 (+Dependency).

  Outstanding gaps after this ship:
    - G5 binary_diff (still &mut Graph but ignored — needs
      single-graph-vs-cross-graph design pass).
